---
import config from '../../site.json';
---
<section id="about" class="py-24 px-6 lg:px-12">
  <div class="container mx-auto">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <!-- Image -->
      <div class="fade-in-up">
        <div class="bg-base-200 rounded-3xl aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden border border-base-300/50">
          <img
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1582213782179-e0d53f98f2ca?w=800&h=600&fit=crop"
            alt="Rise Together team and community members"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Text -->
      <div class="fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
        <span class="badge badge-outline border-primary text-primary text-xs tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">Our Story</span>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-bold mb-6">Built on the<br /><span class="text-primary">Belief</span> That We Rise Together</h2>
        <p class="text-base-content/70 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Founded in 2018 in the heart of Atlanta, Rise Together started as a small group of neighbors who saw unmet needs in their community and decided to act. What began with weekend tutoring sessions in a church basement has grown into a full-service nonprofit serving thousands.
        </p>
        <p class="text-base-content/70 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Our mission is simple: create pathways to opportunity through education, mentorship, and direct community action. We believe that when one person rises, we all rise.
        </p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
          {config.values.map((value) => (
            <div class="bg-primary/5 border border-primary/20 rounded-xl p-4 text-center">
              <p class="font-heading font-semibold text-primary text-sm">{value}</p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
